metadata.name: How to Avoid Getting The Bends – Super Ai Sphere
metadata.description: “How to avoid getting the bends” is an immersive digital experience, designed based on the text of Vanessa Kowalski, a curator, and poet based in New York. The text explores the vision of a dystopian future, based on the predictions of the Right and Left Accelerationists. The work is a monument to what once was humanity.
